def callback(study, trial):
    if study.best_trial.number == trial.number:
        study.set_user_attr(key="best_booster", value=trial.user_attrs["best_booster"])

def objective(trial):
    
    model = CatBoostRegressor(
        #task_type="GPU",        
        iterations=trial.suggest_int("iterations", 400, 1200),
        learning_rate=trial.suggest_float("learning_rate", 1e-3, 1, log=True),
        depth=trial.suggest_int("depth", 4, 10),
        subsample=trial.suggest_float("subsample", 0.05, 1.0),
        colsample_bylevel=trial.suggest_float("colsample_bylevel", 0.05, 1.0),
        min_data_in_leaf=trial.suggest_int("min_data_in_leaf", 1, 100),
        verbose=False,
        random_seed=trial.suggest_categorical("random_seed", [RANDOM_STATE]),
    )
    trial.set_user_attr(key="best_booster", value=model)
    
    
    scores = cross_val_score(model, X_train, y_train, scoring= 'neg_root_mean_squared_error' , cv=cv, n_jobs=-1)
    
    return np.mean(scores)*(-1)

In [36]:



     


def objective(trial):
    alpha = trial.suggest_float("alpha", 1e-5, 100, log=True)
    model_type = trial.suggest_categorical("model_type", ["ridge", "lasso"])

    if model_type == "ridge":
        model = Ridge(alpha=alpha, random_state=RANDOM_STATE)
    else:
        model = Lasso(alpha=alpha, random_state=RANDOM_STATE)


    trial.set_user_attr(key="best_booster", value=model)
    scores = cross_val_score(model, X_train, y_train, scoring= 'neg_root_mean_squared_error' , cv=cv, n_jobs=-1)
    
    return np.mean(scores)*(-1)

In [41]:



     


def objective(trial):
    
    model = LGBMRegressor(
        metric='rmse', 
        random_state=RANDOM_STATE,
        n_estimators=trial.suggest_int('n_estimators', 1000, 10000),
        reg_alpha=trial.suggest_float('reg_alpha', 1e-4, 10.0,log=True),
        reg_lambda=trial.suggest_float('reg_lambda', 1e-4, 10.0,log=True),
        colsample_bytree=trial.suggest_float('colsample_bytree', 0.3, 1.0),
        subsample=trial.suggest_float('subsample', 0.5, 1.0),
        learning_rate=trial.suggest_float('learning_rate', 0.005, 0.2,log=True),
        max_depth=trial.suggest_int('max_depth', 4, 8),
        num_leaves=trial.suggest_int('num_leaves', 40, 100),
        min_child_samples=trial.suggest_int('min_child_samples', 1, 100),
        cat_smooth=trial.suggest_int('cat_smooth', 1, 100)
    )
    trial.set_user_attr(key="best_booster", value=model)
    
    
    scores = cross_val_score(model, X_train, y_train, scoring= 'neg_root_mean_squared_error' , cv=cv, n_jobs=-1)
    
    return np.mean(scores)*(-1)
